ess to many other transport links. Offering guests an opportunity to travel further a field. With its city centre location it gives easy access to many of the city's famous sights. This combined with comfortable and spacious accommodation make the Fiera the perfect base for a trip to Bologna. Fiera has 92 air-conditioned rooms, all equipped with private bathroom, telephone, television with colour and satellite channels, radio, computer/FAX hook ups and mini bar. Non-smoking rooms are available and room service is provided. On hotter days guests have the opportunity to relax away from the sun in the fully air-conditioned hotel. The best way to start the day is with a Fiera breakfast served in the blight and airy breakfast room. The Fiera also has a popular in house restaurant, Il Mercante offers delicious dishes of the Italian tradition along with a choice of the international cuisine. Seating is available for up to 120 people. The hotels comfortable lobby bar is an ideal place to relax and enjoy the large choice of cocktails and drink, served by the barman""Elvis"". For business guests there is an opportunity to make use of the meeting rooms and large variety of meeting facilities. The hotel also offers a sizeable parking and garage facility.With such great transport links and excellent location this is ideal lodgings for both business and pleasure guests.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MoneyExchange</Code><Text>Money exchange</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>PublicInternetAccess</Code><Text>Public internet access</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>LaundryService</Code><Text>Laundry service</Text>